{"descriptions":[{"id":1273,"title":null,"content":"\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eThis construction appears in several expressions consisting of the pronoun \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགང་\u003c/span\u003e (\u0026ldquo;what,\u0026rdquo; \u0026ldquo;as much\u0026rdquo;) followed by an adjective or, sometimes, a verb or an adverb, usually doubled.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགང་མགྱོགས་མགྱོགས་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;As quickly as possible\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགང་ཡག་ཡག་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;As well as possible\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགང་མང་མང་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;As many as possible\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགང་གཟབ་གཟབ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;As carefully as possible\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགང་ཡོད་ཡོད་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;As much as possible\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eWe also find \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགང་\u003c/span\u003e in several constructions such as:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགང་ཐུབ་ཅི་ཐུབ་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;As much as possible\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགང་བྱུང་མང་བྱུང་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Anyhow,\u0026rdquo; \u0026ldquo;indiscriminately\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགང་ལ་གང་འཚམས་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;As appropriate,\u0026rdquo; \u0026ldquo;as convenient\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e","source_url":null,"is_primary":true,"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:24 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:24 UTC","authors":[{"id":"6","fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre"}]}]}